	<h1 >Want to be published?</h1>
	
	Got thoughts you want to share with the world? Some ideas of interest to people starting up their first
	online shop? Share your thoughts with the world, have your articles and blog posts published on this site.
	<p>
	We are particularly interested in detailed reviews of shopping carts. If you've deployed a shopping cart,
	and want to share your experiences of that cart with the world, let us know, there's a good chance we'll be
	interested.
	</p>
	<p>
	What's in it for you? We can offer the following:
	<ul>
		<li>A highly specialised readership of tens of thousands of people a month</li>
		<li>You can include a by line, promoting your self as an expert in your field</li>
		<li>You can include a reasonable number of links to your shop, company homepage or other
		appropriate links. However, we aren't after shallow plugs for your services - real content
		only please
		</li>
		<li>Links from a highly authoritative site.</li>
	</ul>
	</p>
	<p>
	What do we need from you?
	<ul>
		<li>300 - 600 words</li>
		<li>An image to complement the article, approximately 250px wide, 150 - 400px high.</li>
		<li>Up to 2 links</li>
		<li>No links to spammy, overly commercial sites, or sites way off topic</li>
		<li>Preferred delivery format is clean (x)HTML. <a href="http://word2cleanhtml.com/">Word2CleanHTML</a> is a great way to convert word documents</li>
		<li>Quality writing. If your writing is poor quality, badly edited or similar, it will likely be rejected without comment. </li>
	</ul>
	<p>
	Interested? Send an email to <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#274a46554c45674244484a4a42554442545748530944484a"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="9cf1fdeef7fedcf9fff3f1f1f9eefff9efecf3e8b2fff3f1">[email&#160;protected]</span></a>.
	</p>
	<p>
	Note that we welcome balanced articles written by vendor of shopping cart software. However, we will of course
	not publish reviews of your	own software :)
	</p>


					
